<C>__{news reporter}
<D>__{alleged child murderer fred krueger was released on a legal technicality but later burned to death at the hands of a vigilante mob of grieving parents. some years later, a rash of bizarre and unexplainable teen age deaths began leaving many in the area to wonder... is freddy really dead?}
<A>__{meagan's younger sister lizzy comes down to breakfast. the microwave dings and meagan's mom pulls out three pop tarts, dealing them out to her family like playing cards. lizzy picks up her pop tart, whining.}
